<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kopparakecaripaṉmarkku yāṇṭu
<lb n="2"/><num value="16"><g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num> Āvatu kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi> yam ciṟupaḻuvū 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>r tiruvālamtuṟai <hi rend="grantha">m(ā) hā</hi>tevaṟkku <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kā<hi rend="grantha">ryya</hi> m Ārā<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied>kiṟa
<lb n="4"/>kau<hi rend="grantha">śi</hi> kaṉ nakkaṉ māṟapirāṉ Ārā<supplied reason="omitted">ṭ</supplied>ciyil paḻuvū
<lb n="5" break="no"/>r Avaṉikantaṟppapurattu vīracoḻavaṇukka
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉ kuṇavaṉ nākaṉ vacca cantiviḷakku <unclear>mun</unclear>ṟu kā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lai <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Iravum <unclear>pakalum Ākap</unclear> paṉṉiraṇṭukku
<lb n="8" break="no"/>m vaitta poṉ pati(ṉ)ṉeḻu kaḻañcuma
<lb n="9"/>koṇṭu <hi rend="grantha">sandhi</hi> viḷakku panniraṇṭu <unclear>nakkaṉ</unclear><note n="284-1">This inscription is a fragment.</note>
</p>

